<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Landing Page</h1>
<p> Please log into the relevant account  (see db:seed)</p>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Admin:</h2>

<ul class="list-disc pl-6">
  <li class="mb-4">
    <p class="text-lg">Can perform all tasks such as upload/edit/delete videos, upload/edit/delete thumbnail</p>
  </li>
  <li class="mb-4">
    <p class="text-lg">Can create / edit / delete organisations <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">(Bonus)</span></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p class="text-lg">Can add/delete users <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">(Bonus)</span></p>
  </li>
</ul>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Staff:</h2>

<ul class="list-disc pl-6">
  <li class="mb-4">
    <p class="text-lg">Staff can view all pages but can only edit/upload thumbnails</p>
  </li>
  <li class="mb-4">
    <p class="text-lg">Staff should not be able to delete any object</p>
  </li>
  <li class="mb-4">
    <p class="text-lg">Staff can edit organisation details <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">(Bonus)</span></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p class="text-lg">Staff can edit users details but canâ€™t delete them
      <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">(Bonus)</span></p>
  </li>
</ul>

<div class="bg-gray-200 p-4">
<% unless current_user %>
  <%= link_to "login", new_user_session_path, class: "no-underline bg-blue-500 text-white py-2 px-4" %>
<% else %>
  <p> To view your organisation and add and upload videos please sign in</p>
  <%= link_to "View Organisation", organisations_path,
              class: "bg-blue-500 text-white py-2 px-4 no-underline" %>
  <%= link_to "View Video", videos_path,
              class: "bg-blue-500 text-white py-2 px-4 no-underline" %>
<% end %>
</div>
